{"tid":37614,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"落車拍卡冇拉手掣　內地女撞毀賓利","createTime":"2016-12-13T12:25:49.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T05:24:31.000Z","uid":49648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"71dced5aa7f282b708a0967ac6371eb9dd3da5f6","tid":37614,"uid":49648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T12:25:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20161213/bkn-20161213192206566-1213_00982_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20161213%2Fbkn-20161213192206566-1213_00982_001.html&d=Y2AxbamCx9FBq%2F8O3bFsAQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=746cc709\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20161213/bkn-20161213192206566-1213_00982_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=Y2AxbamCx9FBq%2F8O3bFsAQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=4b0aa2fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a> 東網專訊】停車場閘機的擺放位置並唔係部部都咁就手，有啲仲衰到要落車拍卡，幾咁唔方便。不過，離開駕駛席前記得拉手掣（或啟用電子手掣），否則就好似片中呢位女士咁慘慘豬，將部賓利（Bentley）Flying Spur撞毀。據報，意外發生在重慶一個停車場，駕駛者似乎「駛過龍」過了讀卡機，需要落車拍卡，怎料車子突然溜前，直至撞牆才停下，車頭撞毀都幾嚴重。有網民質疑司機有否駕駛執照，連最基本的停車位置都控制不了，落車又唔用泊車手掣，你又點睇？"},{"pid":"91c630f8dac8b7a675422c139385d6870b63cb30","tid":37614,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T12:27:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c478c14d75f1bbb073e80c43cb87464b0334d5cc","tid":37614,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T12:30:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/100010103203496/videos/334745736872197/ \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100010103203496%2Fvideos%2F3347457368721